text: Ic Æthelnoð sacerd an þes landes æt Basyngum mid ealra þæra landes þæt me cining Edmund sealde into niwan ministre on Wintanceacestre <minra> sawla þearfe æc to fremdon & mæge ut to seallan mid ealra freogdom þæt me cining Edmund giefan habban.
Gewitenesse Eadred cining, Æthelgar biscop & Ælfric biscop & menigfeald oþæra manna.
